OL,3,CMike Ashley takes Newcastle United to
OL,4,Ccourt in row over kit sales
OL,6,FAt a hearing in the Competition
OL,7,FAppeal's Tribunal in London today
OL,8,F(Tuesday 9 April 2024), the store was
OL,9,Fdescribed by its lawyers as "the home
OL,10,Fof football", known for its
OL,11,F"competitive pricing".
OL,13,FThe shirt is one of the country's
OL,14,Fbiggest sellers, and the new Adidas
OL,15,Fstrip, which will launch in the
OL,16,Fsummer, is expected to be hugely
OL,17,Fpopular.
