OL,3,CMike Ashley takes Newcastle United to
OL,4,Ccourt in row over kit sales
OL,6,FLawyers for Sports Direct told judges
OL,7,Fan "exclusive" UK deal has instead
OL,8,Fbeen struck with its big rival JD
OL,9,FSports - a move which it claims breaks
OL,10,Fcompetition rules.
OL,12,FSports Direct says roughly 60% of
OL,13,Ftotal sales happen around the time of
OL,14,Fa kit launch before the new season,
OL,15,Fbut that the annual order the company
OL,16,Fplaced for this summer was refused -
OL,17,Fpotentially damaging its revenue and
OL,18,Fits reputation.
