OL,3,CMike Ashley takes Newcastle United to
OL,4,Ccourt in row over kit sales
OL,6,FDescribing Sports Direct as a "gorilla
OL,7,Fin the marketplace", the club's
OL,8,Flawyers told the hearing that teams
OL,9,Flike Leicester, Leeds and Celtic,
OL,10,Falong with the Scottish and Welsh
OL,11,FFootball Associations, already have
OL,12,Fsimilar arrangements to the one
OL,13,FNewcastle United wants to put in place.
OL,15,FThe hearing was also told that Sports
OL,16,FDirect had put in place an agreement
OL,17,Fwith Glasgow Rangers to be the only
OL,18,Fbig high street store supplying its
OL,19,Fnew kit for the lucrative month after
OL,20,Fits launch.
