OL,3,CMike Ashley takes Newcastle United to
OL,4,Ccourt in row over kit sales
OL,6,FNewcastle United's new owners are
OL,7,Finsistent that they have every right
OL,8,Fto take the new shirt from the old
OL,9,Fowners back and sell it through
OL,10,Fsomeone else.
OL,12,FThe judge heard from the Sports Direct
OL,13,Flegal team that excluding the store
OL,14,Ffrom selling the jersey would be
OL,15,F"consumer harming" as it would cut out
OL,16,Fthe retailer "that offers consumers
OL,17,Fthe lowest prices".
