OL,3,CMike Ashley takes Newcastle United to
OL,4,Ccourt in row over kit sales
OL,6,FNewcastle United's representatives
OL,7,Fdismissed that, and said their
OL,8,Fproposed system would see shirts sold
OL,9,Findependently by JD Sports, the club's
OL,10,Fown outlets, and Adidas would provide
OL,11,Fa form of effective competition.
OL,13,FThe hearing today was the first step
OL,14,Fin this legal battle, with Sports
OL,15,FDirect's lawyers effectively seeking
OL,16,Fto implement an injunction to stop
OL,17,Fthis new arrangement, pending a more
OL,18,Fdetailed trial into the matter.
OL,20,FThe outcome of that application will
OL,21,Fbe returned at a later date.
